  "2026-07-04T20:40:45.207Z",maintainer-agent,"Evidence — extended static-quality-gate with documentedSourceFiles (src+packages scope), exported-const coverage, checkExportedMemberDocstringCoverage, and checkTrivialDocstrings. Gate spec now 49 tests, verified 100% lines/branches/functions/statements on the gate script. Trivial-stub check calibrated to ZERO false positives across the ~2783 existing docstrings. Gate reports 3957 missing across 188 files (19 package module docs, 366 exported incl consts, 3572 members) for the sibling fill tasks."
  "2026-07-04T21:37:22.370Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: static gate remains 100% by default while package lint ratchets to current docstring baseline during the fill-work lane. pnpm lint passed; standalone full coverage passed 5371 tests at 100/100/100/100."
